                Mr. Ellis Smith
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ba492901-8b70-4d4d-b56a-83297024056b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
