<p class="">I never mentioned the word "flag" or "showing the flag" in the whole of my lengthy discourse.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-24a9f51d-0a10-4c54-b676-227f29ad9ef9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
