<p class="">I hope the hon. Member will also recognise that it was thanks to Lord Killearn's firm action that we had a friendly Government in Egypt when Marshal Rommel marched in Alexandria.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
