                Mr. Crossman
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9570def8-7830-44bf-a6a7-0727747fd1bf" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-07-30/debates/d42211bd-a56e-4ff4-97b0-5ed3d0df723b/ForeignAffairs(MiddleEast)#contribution-9570def8-7830-44bf-a6a7-0727747fd1bf">
