<p class="">Would not the hon. Gentleman agree that the conflict between India and Pakistan was inevitable when the Government skedaddled out of India without settling the fate of Kashmir and Hyderabad? It was inevitable that those two countries would come into conflict.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
