            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-1ca76c48-e897-44b1-aef1-c810b6a69738">
                Mr. Janner  (Leicester. North-West)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1ca76c48-e897-44b1-aef1-c810b6a69738" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
