<p class="">As my right hon. Friends on the front Bench say, I should like notice of that question. The present position is that the oil refineries are British interests and I am not sure what would be the point of view of my right hon. Friends in regard to any suggestions I might make for internationalising them.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
