        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-4ec17688-d041-4ba8-bb16-f476ef272889">
                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-4ec17688-d041-4ba8-bb16-f476ef272889" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-07-30/debates/d42211bd-a56e-4ff4-97b0-5ed3d0df723b/ForeignAffairs(MiddleEast)#contribution-4ec17688-d041-4ba8-bb16-f476ef272889">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">And the right hon. Gentleman was able to interject his "Yes, Sir," in the monologue of the Chancellor of the Exchequer.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-4ec17688-d041-4ba8-bb16-f476ef272889" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-07-30/debates/d42211bd-a56e-4ff4-97b0-5ed3d0df723b/ForeignAffairs(MiddleEast)#contribution-4ec17688-d041-4ba8-bb16-f476ef272889">
